Package: media-analyzer
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends},
         libqt5widgets5 | libqt6widgets6
Description: Media file analysis tool
 A Qt-based application for analyzing media files,
 providing detailed information about video/audio formats and codecs.

Package: dfm-plugin-media-analyzer
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends},
         media-analyzer (= ${binary:Version}),
         dde-file-manager,
         ffmpeg
Description: DDE file manager media analysis plugin
 Provides dynamic, stream-aware context menu integration for
 media file analysis, preview and conversion in the Deepin File Manager.
 Supports per-category menus for video, audio and image files.

Package: dfm-xmenu-media-analyzer
Architecture: all
Depends: media-analyzer,
         dde-file-manager,
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: DDE file manager context menu integration for media-analyzer (legacy)
 Adds media-analyzer options to the context menu of DDE file manager.
 .
 This is the legacy xmenu plugin. Consider using dfm-plugin-media-analyzer
 instead for dynamic stream-aware menus.

Package: nautilus-xmenu-media-analyzer
Architecture: all
Depends: media-analyzer,
         nautilus (>= 42),
         python3-gi,
         gir1.2-nautilus-3.0
Description: Nautilus file manager context menu integration for media-analyzer
 Adds Media Analyzer options to the right-click menu in Nautilus file manager.

Package: media-analyzer-dbus
Architecture: all
Depends: media-analyzer (= ${source:Version}),
         python3-gi,
         python3-pydbus,
         python3
Description: dbus integration for media-analyzer
 Adds Media Analyzer options to the session dbus.
